dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile contains a bounding box for the world represented in the WGS 84 geographic coordinate system. This layer is part of the Natural Earth Collection (v.2.0.0). Scale: 1:110,000,000. Natural Earth is a public domain map dataset available at 1:10m, 1:50m, and 1:110 million scales. Featuring tightly integrated vector and raster data, with Natural Earth you can make a variety of visually pleasing, well-crafted maps with cartography or GIS software. Kelso, N.V. and Patterson, T. (2012). WGS 84 Bounding Box, World, 1:110 million, 2012. Made with Natural Earth, online at http://www.naturalearthdata.com.
